  intrinsic riskiness of the institution. The ECB performs the impact
  assessment on a yearly basis while the assessment of the risk
  profile of each LSI is performed on a quarterly basis, with LSIs
  identified as most risky defined as 'high-risk LSIs'. (ECB
  Supervisory Manual, page 113)
